content: How much do I owe in taxes?

Tax rate,Taxable income threshold
3.50%, on the portion of taxable income that is $19580 or less, plus
4.40%, on the portion of taxable income over $19580 up to $39150 plus
5.30%, on the portion of taxable income over $39150 up to $431060 plus
7.65%, on the portion of taxable income over $431060
